  "title": "Temp Pharmacy Assistant (6 months/ Entry) #HZO",
  "description": "<p>Salary: $2000 <br />Duration: 6 months <br />Working Hours: 5.5 days office hours</p><p>Location: Tampines North</p><p><strong>Job Scope: </strong></p><p>• Performs picking/packing of medications under Bin Coding System</p><p>• Supports Medication Delivery Service (MDS) and PILBOX/EZYBOX Services for remote collection of medications</p><p>• Assists in patient management of Scriptless Dispensing workflow</p><p>Job Requirements: <br /></p><ul><li>Min. Diploma in any field </li><li>Fully vaccinated if not willing to undergo vaccination</li></ul><p><br />For interested applicants, please send your updated resume to: melissa@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>All candidates’ information will be treated with the strictest confidence</p><p>Melissa Zhang Zhiqi (Mezzo)</p><p>R2197564</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>99C4599</p>",
